            "answer_text": "The sum of interior angles inside the triangle is [math]\\displaystyle 180\u00b0  \\tag*{}[/math]  [math]\\displaystyle 2x:3x:5x \\tag*{}[/math] [math]\\displaystyle 2x+3x+5x=180\u00b0 \\tag*{}[/math] [math]\\displaystyle 10x=180\u00b0 \\tag*{}[/math] [math]\\displaystyle x=18\u00b0 \\tag*{}[/math] Their original ration is then, [math]\\displaystyle 36\u00b0:54\u00b0:90\u00b0 \\tag*{}[/math] ",
